{"tid":798940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公道講，香港搞到炒樓行先，有料做副選，等等亂局，香港人自己都要反醒","createTime":"2018-08-29T16:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T05:43:02.000Z","uid":102240,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b2681e53532d8b505b651d836f7aeeb787d77122","tid":798940,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"預左有人話呢個post分化香港人，或者講中國點樣影響香港<br />\n<br />\n但好多野無人拎枝鎗枝住香港人個頭做，有d野你反抗唔到，唔代表香港人要隨波逐流<br />\n<br />\n炒樓呢個遊戲，幾多香港中產enjoy！幾多香港師奶大A公居屋都拎黎炒！懶理得其他香港人無屋住！香港人為左個仔踢走另一個香港仔！仲有卑視搵唔到錢既大學科目，fg比人壓價，反對加假期減工時，以上種種野，邊個國家邊個政府渣鎗捉住你做？<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得香港呢架水深火熱，除左反抗，自己都應該唔好製造社會問題"},{"pid":"74a58d444d6541e356ed991a27cc3dc45d0560cc","tid":798940,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/000649_eeaac619666321877802b1d3f1be7892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F000649_eeaac619666321877802b1d3f1be7892.png&h=6a9bb922&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/000650_63d725256a5f19e4b07cb55aa9afed3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F000650_63d725256a5f19e4b07cb55aa9afed3e.png&h=fb662ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/000651_d0e258c685a1f78e7b7dfe8cacba6b0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F000651_d0e258c685a1f78e7b7dfe8cacba6b0d.png&h=40883e7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a31b53839afca559112e0963a446da835f4cc667","tid":798940,"uid":33886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"因果調轉左囉 <br />\n雖然我唔係話幫自己 但如果供應夠邊有得炒 你鬼佬唔係唔炒樓 而係跟本冇得炒 有得炒咪一樣當投資產品咁炒 世界就係咁<br />\n<br />\n住呢啲必需品 供應夠 係政府既責任 唔好轉移視線"},{"pid":"8802b154b08d761b286a80f035136ce4f1509df5","tid":7